           CALL WS-PGMID
                USING VIAL0001-COMMAREA VIAL0002-COMMAREA
              ON EXCEPTION
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-ARQ   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE VIAK0001-TRN-NOTFND  TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                MOVE WS-PGMID             TO VIAL0001-CONTEXT-1
           END-CALL.
